N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 36-3.1 - Application

State Regulations

The provisions of Subpart 36-3 shall take precedence over
the provisions for general application in Subpart 36-2 wherever they may differ
from the latter. In the absence of anything to the contrary in Subpart 36-3, the pertinent provisions of Subpart 36-2 will apply. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
